title: Aw Yeah! Comics 01-06 (2013- |Digital-Empire) [REQUESTED]
description:
To quote from the (successfully funded) Kickstarter page that announced this project - Aw Yeah! Comics is..."A NEW line of All-Reader friendly comic books from the minds of Eisner and Harvey Award winning cartoonists Art Baltazar & Franco!"

The series is fun, with great characters and stupendous art, and the series was just recently nominated for an Eisner Award. This pack is a great way to catch up on all the good humor and entertainment!

Aw. Yeah.

All six issues are digital copies thanks to Empire. This fills a request from KAT. Please seed, and enjoy! :-)
